<div>
	When using the #firstname# token in the newsletter, for site members the token will be replaced by the first name from the user profile if populated otherwise it will use the display name from the user profile.</div>
<div>
	&nbsp;</div>
<div>
	For non site members will be replaced by the First Name Token Default setting on the newsletter definition or empty string if not populated.</div>
